  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, garlic, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "3. Add the lamb cubes to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "4. Thread the lamb cubes onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "5. Grill the skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, or until the lamb is cooked through.",
    "6. Transfer the skewers to a plate and garnish with chopped parsley.",
    "7. Serve immediately and enjoy!"
